text:
{
  "prompt": "A streamlined electric delivery scooter designed for urban environments. It features an aerodynamic front cowl and a clear windscreen that protects the rider from wind. The rear has a specially designed vortex-reducing delivery box with a curved surface to minimize drag. The overall design emphasizes stability, comfort, and high efficiency for long delivery rides. Include functional LED lighting and a modern, clean color scheme like white and dark gray with subtle red accents.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A concept design of a front cargo compartment integrated into an electric delivery motorcycle. The motorcycle has a sleek, aerodynamic body, low center of gravity with a skateboard-style battery pack, and a front cowl that includes a built-in insulated food storage compartment. Show two technical-style views: front view and side view (right side). The storage box is seamlessly blended into the front cowl, with a subtle lid for opening. Include details like handlebars, headlight integrated into the cowl, small front wheel, and rear box minimized. Emphasize smooth lines and utilitarian yet modern aesthetic, suitable for urban food delivery.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A simplified ergonomic and legal reference diagram for motorcycle or electric scooter riding posture. The diagram should include a side view of a rider on a two-wheeled vehicle, showing the following key dimensions labeled: seat height, handlebar reach, footrest position, knee angle, back angle, and eye level. Include simplified annotations showing legal limitations (e.g., seat height range 740-800mm, handlebar height not above shoulder, proper foot positioning). The style should be clean and schematic, like a textbook or instructional guide illustration.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A simplified ergonomic schematic diagram of a riding position for an electric motorcycle. The rider is shown with a slightly reclined back, knees extended more forward than a standard scooter position, and with a supportive pelvic rest integrated into the seat. The arms reach naturally to handlebars. The posture is designed for long-distance comfort and low fatigue. Use minimalistic 2D vector-style illustration on a neutral background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A technical side-view line drawing of a modern electric scooter designed for delivery, featuring a low riding position. The rider is depicted with legs extended more forward than usual, almost like a cruiser bike, and sitting in a comfortable position with a pelvis-supporting seat. The overall design focuses on ergonomic riding posture with feet-forward leg positioning, resembling a relaxed and efficient delivery vehicle layout. The drawing emphasizes human proportions and riding posture alignment.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 2D digital technical illustration of an ergonomic riding position for an electric delivery motorcycle. The rider is seated in a relaxed, forward-leaning posture with legs extended forward and feet resting on a foot platform near the front wheel. The wheelbase of the motorcycle is extended, and the rider’s position is shifted closer to the center of both wheels, with the silhouette of the rider aligned with the center axis of the front and rear wheels. The frame includes a built-in back support at the pelvis. The design is minimalist, with a focus on low center of gravity and aerodynamic efficiency.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A semi-recumbent electric delivery motorcycle, redesigned for ergonomic comfort. The rider is in a relaxed, semi-reclined position with feet extended forward. The frame features a low-slung seat with back support (hip-supporting seat), extended wheelbase, and a skate-style battery pack integrated under the seat. The front has a modest cowling with built-in storage compartment for food delivery. The handlebars are positioned mid-height, allowing relaxed arm posture. The overall design prioritizes low center of gravity, aerodynamic efficiency, and urban practicality. The illustration is a clean, technical side profile drawing with a realistic and modern industrial style.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A futuristic electric delivery scooter designed for extreme aerodynamic performance. The vehicle features a semi-recumbent riding position, a low-profile front nose integrated with minimalist headlights, smooth teardrop-shaped body lines, and a fully enclosed underbelly battery compartment. The rear of the scooter includes an integrated delivery box designed to blend with the aerodynamics, and the wheels are partially covered with fairings. The entire design is sleek and modern, resembling a fusion between a sportbike and a delivery scooter, emphasizing low wind resistance and lightweight construction.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A technical side view sketch of an aerodynamic electric maxi-scooter with a streamlined design. The front of the scooter features a visible air duct vent with adjustable louver fins, designed to open and close for battery cooling. The scooter has a low profile, semi-recumbent riding position, large front and rear fairings, and integrated battery housing under the floorboard. The sketch should emphasize airflow lines and show how the front air intake contributes to cooling. Include a clean, technical line art style.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A side profile technical line drawing of a modern electric delivery scooter with integrated aerodynamic design. The front features an adjustable air duct vent for battery cooling. The rear section includes a built-in storage compartment large enough to fit two large pizza boxes side-by-side. The storage is seamlessly integrated into the body of the scooter, with smooth contours and a secure latch system. The scooter has a low-slung aerodynamic profile, semi-recumbent riding position, and a long wheelbase. The overall look is sleek and futuristic.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A modern electric delivery scooter designed with a skateboard-style low center battery pack. Above the battery pack, there's a sleek, integrated cargo box designed to fit two large pizza boxes. The scooter is shown in side view, featuring aerodynamic fairings, a semi-recumbent rider position, and vented front ducts for battery cooling. The overall design is lightweight and futuristic, optimized for urban food delivery.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 2D side-view technical illustration of a modern scooter inspired by the Honda Ruckus design, featuring an integrated cargo compartment under the seat frame. The cargo space is enclosed within a hard box attached beneath the seat, blending seamlessly with the frame structure. The battery is placed under the footboard (skateboard-style), and the overall design maintains a rugged and minimalist aesthetic. The drawing should show clear structural outlines, including wheels, handlebar, seat, and cargo box, in a clean line-art schematic style.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A futuristic electric scooter designed for food delivery, featuring a front aerodynamic cargo box integrated with the scooter's fairing. The cargo box is shaped like a teardrop (aerodynamic), placed just above the headlight and below the windscreen. The scooter has a sleek, modern design with smooth curves, optimized for urban delivery. The illustration shows a side view and a 3/4 front view in technical line art style, minimal color, and high detail to emphasize form and function.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A simplified CFD (Computational Fluid Dynamics) diagram of an aerodynamic electric scooter designed for delivery, side view. The scooter features a fully enclosed fairing, a low-riding semi-recumbent rider position, and a streamlined front top box integrated into the front cowling. Arrows and flow lines indicate smooth airflow over the surfaces, with minimal turbulence at the rear. The bottom of the scooter includes an underbody cover, and wheel covers are present to reduce drag. The image should have a clean, technical look with transparent airflow lines and a monochrome background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A sleek 3D rendering of an electric delivery scooter with a long nose short tail design. The front features an aerodynamic extended nose with integrated windscreen and LED headlight. A central air duct is built into the front fairing for battery cooling. The rider sits in a semi-recumbent position with a lumbar support. The battery is housed in a flat skateboard-style compartment under the floorboard for low center of gravity. The rear is short and minimalist with exposed suspension and a compact LED tail light. The overall design is inspired by a sports car's aerodynamic principles.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A highly detailed technical digital illustration of an electric scooter with oversized wheels (front 19-inch, rear 17-inch), full suspension, and a low deck with a long wheelbase. The frame includes a streamlined integrated battery pack in a skateboard-style design, and now includes a comfortable ergonomic seat with back support, allowing the rider to sit instead of stand. The riding position is semi-recumbent, optimized for long-distance urban delivery. The front fairing includes aerodynamic panels and an integrated windscreen. The overall design is futuristic, minimalist, and optimized for aerodynamics and comfort.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A side-view technical illustration of an electric scooter designed with a skateboard-style battery pack at the base. Above the battery is a wide, flat foot platform for the rider. The design emphasizes spacious lower body accommodation, with extended room around the legs and feet. The overall frame is low and long for stability, and includes a comfortable seat for seated riding. The image should be clean, minimal, and look like a product concept sketch for industrial design.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A concept design of a modern electric scooter featuring a skateboard-style flat battery pack integrated into the base of the frame. On top of the battery pack is a spacious standing platform for the rider's feet. The design includes a wide and ergonomic lower body area to accommodate the rider's legs comfortably in a seated position. The scooter has a low center of gravity, aerodynamic side panels, and a minimalist urban utility look. Include handlebars, a seat, and large front and rear wheels (19-inch front, 17-inch rear). The frame is optimized for stability and efficiency.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A modern electric scooter design inspired by the minimalist step-through frame in the provided image. Modify the design with a large 21-inch front wheel and a 17-inch rear wheel. Add a sleek aerodynamic front cowl that partially covers the front wheel and integrates a headlight. Maintain the red and white color scheme and overall lightweight structure. Include front and rear suspension, disc brakes, and a modern urban aesthetic.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 3D-rendered electric scooter with a 21-inch front wheel and a 17-inch rear wheel, featuring a modern aerodynamic front cowl and a fully faired seat area integrated into the body. The scooter has a low, skateboard-style battery deck and a large legroom area. The front cowl and seat fairing are designed to enhance airflow and aesthetics, with a cohesive and sleek look. High-resolution, clean white background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 3D-rendered digital image of a modern electric delivery scooter with aerodynamic design. It has a red and white color scheme, a 21-inch front wheel and a 17-inch rear wheel, with a front fairing (cowl) covering the handlebars and front assembly. The seat area is fully faired with smooth panels. Attached to the rear is a sleek, aerodynamic cargo rack shaped with flowing, streamlined curves to match the scooter’s design. The background is plain white for product showcase.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A modern electric scooter with a streamlined, aerodynamic design. It has a 21-inch front wheel and a 17-inch rear wheel. The front section includes a fully integrated aerodynamic front cowl and a large windscreen (windshield) for wind protection. The scooter also features a faired seat section and a sleek, curved rear cargo rack. The design emphasizes smooth lines, aerodynamic performance, and practicality for urban delivery use.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 3D-rendered digital image of a modern electric scooter with a red and white color scheme. The scooter has a streamlined design, large front windshield, aerodynamic rear cargo rack, and a fully faired seating area. The front wheel is 21 inches, and the rear wheel is 17 inches. The legroom area (step-through section) is extended by 10cm for added space. The overall design remains sleek and functional, suitable for urban commuting and delivery purposes.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "An exploded technical diagram of a modern electric scooter showing individual parts and their assembly structure. Include components such as the front fairing, handlebar assembly, front suspension, front and rear wheels (21-inch front, 17-inch rear), central frame with step-through design, mid-drive motor, skateboard-style battery pack, seat, rear shock absorbers, aerodynamic rear cargo rack, and a front windshield. The image should be clean, black and white line drawing style, showing part numbers and connection points clearly.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A detailed 2D technical drawing of a 72V 120Ah lithium-ion battery pack for an electric motorcycle. The illustration shows an exploded view of the pack with 21700 cells arranged in a 20s24p configuration. The drawing includes structural components such as a metal enclosure, thermal pads, aluminum cooling channels, insulation layers, a high-capacity BMS (Battery Management System), cell holders, busbars, and wiring harnesses. The airflow paths for active or passive cooling are marked with arrows. Components are labeled in English. The overall shape is flat and rectangular, optimized for skateboard-style battery placement under the floorboard. Minimal color, blueprint-style on white background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
